The paper focuses on bibliometric evaluation and network analysis of co-authored publications between China and Korea, which falls under the scope of digital libraries (cs.DL), social and information networks (cs.SI), system and database management (cs.SD), information retrieval (cs.IR), and computers and society (cs.CY).
